This paper focuses on deep reinforcement learning in multiagent environments, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper specifically addresses stochastic cooperative environments, which falls under multiagent systems (cs.MA) and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the proposed framework involves a mixture replay strategy, which relates to control systems (cs.SY).
